      &MIXING
          METHOD BROYDEN_MIXING
          ALPHA 0.1
          BETA 1.5
          NBROYDEN 8
      &END
      CHOLESKY OFF
    &END SCF
    &XC
      &XC_FUNCTIONAL PBE0
      &END XC_FUNCTIONAL
      &HF
         &MEMORY
          MAX_MEMORY 22000
         &END MEMORY
      &END HF
